data.description: Location! Location! Location! Look no further than this home close to all the amenities Upper Allen has to offer. Welcome to this very much loved and taken care of comfortable one story home located in the cozy neighborhood of Reservoir Hills. This beautiful all brick ranch home features 3 bedrooms, one full and a half bathrooms, hardwood floors, a recently finished lower level rec room, and ample storage. The owners have had professionally opened the main floor by having removed the dividing wall between the living room and dining/kitchen to expose the stairway to the lower level rec room, making the main level open and bright. Home is on a nice manicured lot featuring a large backyard, and a large patio for outdoor entertainment. Must see!
